                                         "text":  "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgMath13\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMath13', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: In this image, the Equator parallel and the Greenwich Meridian are highlighted, with the intersection at point O</p>",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "006b21c9-6800-4deb-bb3f-a367dd38b703",
                                                            "text":  "NOAA",
